Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, isn't it about time you tell me your thoughts regarding all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given the rather "convenient" interaction between Kira and the Japanese police during this incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the very least, I can conclude that Kira and the Japanese police are working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Working together"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that's true, then Kira is... {\alpha&HFF&}the second-generation L.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that's true, then Kira is... the second-generation L.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.66,0:00:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, {\alpha&HFF&}but I'm only around 7% certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but I'm only around 7% certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Lester, {\alpha&HFF&}when investigating, once you've decided on something,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Lester, when investigating, once you've decided on something,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you must believe in it absolutely, and if you're wrong, then "sorry" should suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:44.60,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(361,360)}Justice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:58.72,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,"Recently, crime has decreased in Japan, because if you do something bad, your name will be put on the Internet, and you'll be killed by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:00:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Name?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:01:01.24,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what my dad says."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.68,0:01:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you give me your name, we can't file a record.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Have mercy! Anything but my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll expose all your names on the Internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:12.38,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,500)}Kira-sama, please kill me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:42.37,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to announce, here and now, that Kira is Justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:46.79,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\fscy0\t(0,700,\fscy100)\pos(353,431)\c&H68C3DD&}Kira's Realm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.49,0:01:55.34,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an undeniable fact that I've been appointed by Kira to be their spokesman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:59.26,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,There may be those who'll attempt to take my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:07.94,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm prepared to lay down my life in order to bring you the words of Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:06.60,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(363,388)}New Japanese Investigative Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kira's Realm"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.96,0:02:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a distasteful title...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this world turning into?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:14.05,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Investigating Kira is an inexcusable thing! I'll even go as far as saying that it's a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd really be better off if they killed this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:21.63,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,The police, members of the public, criminals... whoever's investigating Kira, report them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's time for the President's press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.51,0:02:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's happening? {\alpha&HFF&}They said it's going to be a "message to the world"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's happening? They said it's going to be a "message to the world"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you lot seem to do is watch TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the United States of America...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...hereby acknowledge Kira and will not oppose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Success!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even America is finally accepting Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:02:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}What the hell is he saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell is he saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they fear Kira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. President!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When was this decision made?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give us more details?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that Kira is Justice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"? I'm not saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's a fact that thanks to Kira's powers, war has ceased.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Organized crime, and not just in our own country, has also been obliterated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we openly oppose Kira, we will be killed. That much is certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, while we won't acknowledge them as justice, we'll no longer take any measures to try and catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the same thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you just say that you acknowledge Kira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself this country's representative?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this... {\alpha&HFF&}this is America we're talking about... and that was a presidential statement!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this... this is America we're talking about... {\alpha&HFF&}and that was a presidential statement!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this... this is America we're talking about... and that was a presidential statement!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, can I be serious for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the sudden change?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.34,0:03:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you normally aren't serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really believe, from the depths of your heart, that Kira is evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Matsuda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest... {\alpha&HFF&}I just can't believe that they're completely evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest... I just can't believe that they're completely evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You believe that Kira is Justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I believe that Kira is fighting against evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also an undeniable fact that the world has become a better place for those who live honest lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, Matsuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all just built on the fear of being slaughtered. This isn't real peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! {\alpha&HFF&}I know that much, but... I also understand the feelings of those who proclaim Kira to be their savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I know that much, but... {\alpha&HFF&}I also understand the feelings of those who proclaim Kira to be their savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I know that much, but... I also understand the feelings of those who proclaim Kira to be their savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been in a weak position...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a cop! {\alpha&HFF&}I can't acknowledge Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a cop! I can't acknowledge Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, and I want to catch them, because it's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to be crazy doing this without even being able to fully oppose Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that is crazy, Matsuda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?! Even you, Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Kira must realize that what they're doing is evil; {\alpha&HFF&}yet, they've still decided to sacrifice themselves to change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Kira must realize that what they're doing is evil; yet, they've still decided to sacrifice themselves to change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the type of justice Kira has chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm assuming that's what Kira probably is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not our job to decide whether Kira is good or evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.90,0:05:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only have to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we catch Kira, then Kira is evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira takes control of the world, then Kira is Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, henceforth, things will accelerate and the world will rapidly turn toward Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will definitely become Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.55,0:05:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to us now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll have to disband. Thanks to that chicken of a president.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.83,0:05:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... he's not even a chicken. He's lower than a maggot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a joke. There's no way acknowledging Kira is the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello... {\alpha&HFF&}welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello... welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put the gun down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please lower your guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shedding blood here will only be a waste of our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he killed our colleagues!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't make me say this again and again; {\alpha&HFF&}our objective is to capture Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't make me say this again and again; our objective is to capture Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing Mello now would achieve nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has this gone exactly as you expected it to so far, Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. {\alpha&HFF&}You must have heard it from Lidner... about what happened with the second-generation L.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You must have heard it from Lidner... {\alpha&HFF&}about what happened with the second-generation L.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You must have heard it from Lidner... about what happened with the second-generation L.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to everything you've done, I've been able to narrow down Kira quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a device for you to solve your puzzles with!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello, if you want to shoot me, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello! {\alpha&HFF&}If you shoot Near, we'll have no choice but to shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello! If you shoot Near, {\alpha&HFF&}we'll have no choice but to shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello! If you shoot Near, we'll have no choice but to shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:08:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you both die here, what will that achieve?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll only make Kira happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. {\alpha&HFF&}Near, I only came to get back that photo you have of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Near, I only came to get back that photo you have of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. {\alpha&HFF&}This is the only photo... there are no copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. This is the only photo... {\alpha&HFF&}there are no copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. This is the only photo... there are no copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've dealt with anyone who would have known your face, at Wammy's House and elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say this with 100% certainty, but you won't be killed with that notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you wanted, Mello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of cooperating with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... {\alpha&HFF&}it'd be annoying to leave here with only this photo to show for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... it'd be annoying to leave here with only this photo to show for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer's notebook... {\alpha&HFF&}it's a Shinigami's notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer's notebook... it's a Shinigami's notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who have the notebook can see the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is going to believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can Mello achieve by lying about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he was going to lie, he'd lie about something more meaningful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, Shinigami exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The notebook I had was once in the possession of someone other than a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at least one of the rules written in there is fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's about as much as I can tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which of us will catch Kira first...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a race, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're both heading toward the same goal. {\alpha&HFF&}I'll be there waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're both heading toward the same goal. I'll be there waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Comment: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fake rule...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given what's already happened, things such as heart attacks and being able to manipulate people before their deaths must be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Burning or shredding the notebook"? {\alpha&HFF&}The notebooks still exist and there's no way to test that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Burning or shredding the notebook"? The notebooks still exist and there's no way to test that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fake rule {\alpha&HFF&}must be the one that states you'll die unless you write a name in the notebook within 13 days of the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fake rule must be the one that states you'll die unless you write a name in the notebook within 13 days of the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gevanni, get me L.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, {\alpha&HFF&}we caught Mello... but he got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, we caught Mello... {\alpha&HFF&}but he got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, we caught Mello... but he got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I was able to question him a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you mean he didn't get away, {\alpha&HFF&}you "allowed him" to get away? Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you mean he didn't get away, you "allowed him" to get away? {\alpha&HFF&}Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you mean he didn't get away, you "allowed him" to get away? Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he really did get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, he mentioned that that notebook was bound to a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been able to verify the existence of such a being?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Shinigami do in fact exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you wouldn't believe me even if I told you, so I never said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of things I'd like to ask that Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna be asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What bothers me the most are the rules written in the notebook, and the fact that there may be a fake rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:11:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:11:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, {\alpha&HFF&}I'd like to hear your thoughts on this. If there was a fake rule, which would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, I'd like to hear your thoughts on this. {\alpha&HFF&}If there was a fake rule, which would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, I'd like to hear your thoughts on this. If there was a fake rule, which would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the process of elimination, it would have to be the one that says you'll die if you don't write a name within 13 days of the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you think that after all... {\alpha&HFF&}so do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you think that after all... so do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami, were there any fake rules written in the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. There weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a Shinigami with you, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? {\alpha&HFF&}I think I'm beginning to understand this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? I think I'm beginning to understand this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is there, and is telling the Shinigami to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This dude is amazing. He's spot on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there was a fake, and the Shinigami is lying, it doesn't mean anything, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it would make Light's detainment pointless as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not true that you need to continue to write in the notebook to stay alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then there's no meaning to the fact that he did nothing for 13 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-{\alpha&HFF&}That's different. There's no way Light-kun could be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's different. {\alpha&HFF&}There's no way Light-kun could be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's different. There's no way Light-kun could be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before he died, the Deputy Chief himself confirmed that Light-kun doesn't have a notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, how about we verify it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will write Mello's name in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then if I die 13 days after Mello, {\alpha&HFF&}Kira wins. I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then if I die 13 days after Mello, Kira wins. {\alpha&HFF&}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then if I die 13 days after Mello, Kira wins. I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}What? This is about winning and losing now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What? {\alpha&HFF&}This is about winning and losing now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What? This is about winning and losing now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Verifying the "13 days" rule can only be a positive thing for the Kira investigation. There are no negatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me to lay down my life for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:14:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm the only one to reject this idea, what sort of impression will that give the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us a while. We'll need to discuss this proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like everyone to give me their honest opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We can't do this out of respect for human life"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy for me to say, but I was the one detained, and it'll sound suspicious coming from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange. Killing Mello would avenge the Deputy Chief, so if Near wants to do that, I'm inclined to let him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that no one here is Kira, and ultimately, killing people with the notebook is not something we should be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we should try to follow in the Deputy Chief's footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also against the idea of verifying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, there's no way we can go ahead with verifying the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought... {\alpha&HFF&}Lastly, let me ask you one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought... Lastly, let me ask you one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all of you at the Japanese Investigative Headquarters... {\alpha&HFF&}have you ever thought, even once, that your "second-generation" L might be Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all of you at the Japanese Investigative Headquarters... have you ever thought, even once, {\alpha&HFF&}that your "second-generation" L might be Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all of you at the Japanese Investigative Headquarters... have you ever thought, even once, that your "second-generation" L might be Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anyone there who, having heard the conversation up to this point, is willing to cooperate with my investigation in any way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then ring the number I'm about to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to reach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun can't be Kira. {\alpha&HFF&}No, I don't even want to think that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun can't be Kira. No, {\alpha&HFF&}I don't even want to think that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun can't be Kira. No, I don't even want to think that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the "13 days" rule is fake, he's not completely above suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... {\alpha&HFF&}I've got no choice now but to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... I've got no choice now but to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}Is this some kind of joke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this some kind of joke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you decide when you compare tomorrow's events with the death list I'm about to read you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:16:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. President, first, I'd like to thank you deeply for your approval of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, that's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like you to bring a swift end to the actions of the SPK, the organization out to get Kira, by ordering their dissolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, I would like you to use the police force, CIA,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FBI, and any other secret organizations to determine the whereabouts of the SPK members.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you uncover them, I would like you to tell me immediately via a communication point that I'll specify later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. President, {\alpha&HFF&}whether you live a long life or not, is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. President, whether you live a long life or not, is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demegawa-san! Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you going to New York all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to crush an organization that dares to oppose Kira-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A live report!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:17:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The President dropped me a line under orders from Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I don't know what's going on, and I don't even care!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our viewing figures are going to go up by 100... no, 120%!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, everyone, the age of Kira is upon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The previous L suspected Light-kun too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I was to suggest the need to investigate him again, then if he really is Kira, I'll just be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"13 days" rule, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, {\alpha&HFF&}we've known each other for a long time now... I know what's worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, we've known each other for a long time now... {\alpha&HFF&}I know what's worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, we've known each other for a long time now... I know what's worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to do what you believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never fully trusted L.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:18:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now I'm doing this because I want to work with you, not Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ide...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact Near without Light-kun finding out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you do, I'll ensure that no one finds out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun... {\alpha&HFF&}you're not Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun... you're not Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible! Live on TV, Demegawa's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Demegawa, have finally tracked down the base of an evil organization that seeks to capture our God, Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:19:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and along with my brothers, we have them surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, they appear to be hiding in this building!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Witness the power of the people!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of Justice!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Near comes running out, I'll write his name in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! Misa will give it her best!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... at this rate we really will get dragged out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this one of Mello's plans to destroy the SPK?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or does the SPK operate in such ways that allow even members of the public to track down their location?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... {\alpha&HFF&}how dare you lie to me so blatantly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... how dare you lie to me so blatantly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I win, Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:59.84,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(533,294)}To be continued
